sources.description:
INSTANT JUSTICE POURED FROM THE BLAZING END OF HIS SIX-GUN! 
The Tulliver brothers are terrorizing the town of Heldorado, and Shamrock has been sent to round them up and drive them out.

Watch original Black & White version: https://youtu.be/iB8DOD260Oc
Director: Thomas Carr
Writers: Ron Ormond, Maurice Tombragel, Jack Natteford
Stars:James Ellison, Russell Hayden, Raymond Hatton, Fuzzy Knight, Julie Adams, Tom Tyler
Genre: Classics, Western
